acked-nvidia-dgx-spark\">\n  <p>Autonomous AI agents are driving the next wave of AI innovation. These agents must often manage long-running tasks that use multiple communication channels and background subprocesses simultaneously to explore options, test solutions, and generate optimal results. This places extreme demands on local compute. NVIDIA DGX Spark provides the performance necessary for autonomous agents to execute…</p>\n  <p><a href=\"https://developer.nvidia.com/blog/scaling-autonomous-ai-agents-and-workloads-with-nvidia-dgx-spark/\" rel=\"nofollow\" data-wpel-link=\"internal\" target=\"_self\">Source</a></p>\n </body>\n</html>",
  "aiSummary": "NVIDIA DGX Spark 为自主 AI 智能体提供了执行复杂、长时任务所需的本地计算性能，支持多通信通道和后台子进程。",
  "oneSentenceSummary": "NVIDIA DGX Spark 为自主 AI 智能体提供了执行复杂、长时任务所需的本地计算性能，支持多通信通道和后台子进程。",
  "summary": "本文介绍 NVIDIA DGX Spark 如何通过自主智能体推动下一波 AI 创新。这些先进的 AI 系统需要管理长时运行的任务，同时利用多通信通道和后台子进程来探索选项、测试解决方案并生成最优结果。此类计算密集型工作负载对本地计算资源造成极大压力，而 DGX Spark 正是专门为此而设计。",
